title: DDFP 316 (Pt. II) Nate Burleson & Ryan Kerrigan

description:
Shek is joined by former NFL wide receiver Nate Burleson and Washington Redskins linebacker Ryan Kerrigan to discuss Odell Beckham's rookie year, RGIII's season, Tony Romo's play this year and some holiday caroling.
